description:
This dataset contains individual-level records for freshwater crabs that tested positive for Paragonimus metacercariae during laboratory examinations. The dataset includes sampling location (province, canton, district, locality, river/stream, and geographic coordinates), collection date, elevation, host sex, morphometric measurements, molecular identifiers, PCR results, and the tissue-specific distribution and counts of metacercariae. 
 The dataset was used to support prevalence estimates, parasitological analyses, and figure preparation in the associated study. 
 &nbsp;

